metadata.name: Imperfections
metadata.description:
The work is a screen shot of the Photoshop workspace made while I was working on the photo collage called 𝘓𝘪𝘧𝘦 𝘓𝘪𝘯𝘦. I was happier with the screen shot than the collage itself and decided to keep it.

The bidder will receive the original printable collage, as well as the printable screen shot work.

𝘐𝘮𝘱𝘦𝘳𝘧𝘦𝘤𝘵𝘪𝘰𝘯𝘴: 4000 x 4000 | 300 dpi
𝘓𝘪𝘧𝘦 𝘓𝘪𝘯𝘦: 4959 x 7016 | 300 dpi
